<div class="error-wrap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="error-box error-404">
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <i class="icon icon-sad"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-8">
        <strong>Error,<em>404</em></strong>
        <p>您所查看的也没无法浏览或已经不存在</p>
        <span>输入的地址不正确</span>
        <span>页面重定义或程序出错</span>
        <div class="return">
          <a href="/"> 返回首页 &raquo;</a>  <em class="red" id="digest">5</em> 秒之后页面自动跳转...
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<script>
  window.setTimeout(function(){
    window.location.href="<%= root_url %>"
  }, 5000);
  window.setInterval(function() {
    $("#digest").text($("#digest").text() - 1);
  }, 1000);
</script>
